stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> pending: 用户下单
    pending --> paid: 卖家确认/买家付款
    pending --> cancelled: 超时未付/取消
    paid --> shipped: 卖家发货
    paid --> cancelled: 协商取消
    shipped --> completed: 买家确认收货<br/>或7天自动确认
    shipped --> completed: 自动确认定时任务
    cancelled --> [*]
    completed --> [*]

    note right of pending
        行锁扣库存
        FOR UPDATE
    end note

    note right of completed
        触发评价
        更新月售统计
    end note
